  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join The Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/2c1a65f56db120eed0c68831e738f93c.poster.avif?t=1725989757\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/2c1a65f56db120eed0c68831e738f93c.webm?t=1725989757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/2c1a65f56db120eed0c68831e738f93c.mp4?t=1725989757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore hundreds upon hundreds of <strong>vibrant islands</strong> to take a break, breathe deeply and <strong>snap beautiful photos</strong> with your camera. Lose yourself in the moment while hunting for that one photo you'll remember forever.<br><br><i>Camera in hand, you set out to capture a moment.<br><br>To walk where no one has walked before.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/88df667837f73641bb64907f76a86ccc.avif?t=1725989757\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>No Goal to Reach!</strong> Take as many photos as you like, or just one. You're the only one who can decide what makes a good photo - no grades here! Make it as creative and fun as you can.<br></li><li> <strong>Lose Yourself:</strong> Get lost on vibrant islands, take it slow or explore every nook and cranny of these generated spaces.<br></li><li> <strong>Capture the Magic:</strong> Use a myriad of camera settings and filters to make every picture your own. Share your images or visit islands others have photographed before.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/2c1a65f56db120eed0c68831e738f93c.poster.avif?t=1725989757\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/2c1a65f56db120eed0c68831e738f93c.webm?t=1725989757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/2c1a65f56db120eed0c68831e738f93c.mp4?t=1725989757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore hundreds upon hundreds of <strong>vibrant islands</strong> to take a break, breathe deeply and <strong>snap beautiful photos</strong> with your camera. Lose yourself in the moment while hunting for that one photo you'll remember forever.<br><br><i>Camera in hand, you set out to capture a moment.<br><br>To walk where no one has walked before.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1513480/extras/88df667837f73641bb64907f76a86ccc.avif?t=1725989757\" width=616 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>No Goal to Reach!</strong> Take as many photos as you like, or just one. You're the only one who can decide what makes a good photo - no grades here! Make it as creative and fun as you can.<br></li><li> <strong>Lose Yourself:</strong> Get lost on vibrant islands, take it slow or explore every nook and cranny of these generated spaces.<br></li><li> <strong>Capture the Magic:</strong> Use a myriad of camera settings and filters to make every picture your own. Share your images or visit islands others have photographed before.</li></ul>",
